{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "The hotel is located adjacent to the MTR station of East Tsim Sha Tsui and is connected to the Airport Express by the free shuttle service at Kowloon Station. It is a short walk to the Avenue of Stars promenade and main shopping area of Tsim Sha Tsui/Kowloon.\nCheck in was excellent and I would thoroughly recommend the Harbour Club as this is an oasis of calm in a very busy city.\nOur room was spotlessly clean and very well appointed. The harbour view was amazing. The staff at the hotel were first class, courteous, faultlessly polite and extremely  efficient. We would have liked to have stayed longer and will surely be back.", "date": "Reviewed Jul 11, 2019"}
