{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "My stay in Shangri La Kowloon was incredibly memorable because of the doorman, Allan.  Allan was very welcoming and always had a bright smile to all who entered the hotel.  He made an extra effort to serve the guests. He played with my 7 year old boy and made him very happy.  Because of Allan, my son will only choose Shangri La the next time we visit. We had an ocean view room. The view is breath taking. The dim sum restaurant cross the street, mian cui xuan restaurant, is very yummy.", "date": "Reviewed Jun 18, 2019"}
