{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "Very good", "description": "Close to the harbour and the view is great if you have a harbour view. Be aware that yOu cannot see the entire light show from the site.\r\nThe hop on hop off bus stop us across the road and the train station is close by. The star ferry isn\u2019t far away and it\u2019s a nice walk along the harbour.\r\n\r\nI only had dinner in the restaurant once and I think it was average and very expensive. Try eating locally for reasonable prices. All western restaurants are expensive.", "date": "Reviewed Apr 19, 2019"}
