{"rating_score": "6.0", "rating_badge": "Good", "description": "Room service not up to what I expect from a 5 star property.  Impressive lobby area,  our room was large with great view of HK harbour.  Room probably needs updating.", "date": "Reviewed Apr 21, 2019"}
