{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Dedicated staff from doorman to receptionists to cleaners, floor supervisor, concierge were overtly attention to details. Hardware - attention to scruff marks, no smell to pillows, circulating fans in hallway, availability of ironing board. Service - not just turning of bed cover, also luggage straps on our bags were placed to exact length. Right next to the water and subway station, near great bakery and desert shops. Even melons from Korea and Japan available outside hotel door! Area to improve - very few, but making sure water pot interior be metal, not plastic, would eliminate guest's health concern of presence of plasticizer. Would definitely return to this hotel in future visits to Hong Kong. Thank you for doing such a fantastic job!", "date": "Reviewed Nov 1, 2018"}
