{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Stayed for one night in a club room with Horizon club access to wrap up a week long holiday. Wish I had stayed longer! The service, room and facilities were all excellent, particularly the Horizon club (in all aspects). The surrounding area is also great, with close access to the MTR, local and brand shopping, as well as lots of street food or restaurants to chooee from. Gordon Ramsey's London House is nearby, for which the beef burger is particularly excellent, I cannot recommend it enough! In saying that, the complimentary food and drink offerings available at the Horizon club are certainly more than enough to satisfy in lieu of purchasing a meal out. I didn't eat at any of them, but the restaurants in the hotel came recommended from a few people I spoke to before deciding to stay there too. Great experience all round. ", "date": "Reviewed Oct 23, 2018"}
