{"rating_score": "2.0", "rating_badge": "Poor", "description": "We were surprised when we arrived at the hotel that the air-conditioning was not working. We did hear about the news and called Expedia before our departure and was told that the air-conditioning was working. We did not have a choice but to accept the suggestion to move into another hotel. We think that the air-conditioning was never back on and Shangri-La was not being truthful and misled us because of the concerns of losing business or they were more concerned about business than our interests. \r\nExpedia should be contacted before our arrival that the air-conditioning was out so we could make arrangement prior to our arrival. \r\n", "date": "Reviewed Jul 3, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Would definitely re-visit and highly recommended. Had a pleasant and comfortable stay at Shangri-La hotel in Tsim Sha Tsui during my visit in Hong Kong. ", "date": "Reviewed Jun 27, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "4.0", "rating_badge": "Fair", "description": "The service overrall was not bad but there are so many tourists all around the hotel.\r\nSome customers are not well behaive and stayed up late and shouting running the corridoor etc. This is not 5 star hotel quality of stay.", "date": "Reviewed Jun 11, 2018"}
