{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Amazin", "date": "Reviewed Jun 4, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Great stay! We were a little hesitant to stay in Kowloon as it\u2019s far from the city centre. However, we loved the area much better. HK Island is filled with expats whilst Kowloon is a much more authentic HK experience. The hotel itself was lovely. Very nice rooms with lots of space. We even unpacked our bags - lots of great cupboard space! The hotel offered everything including a warm welcome every time we walked in. We just loved it and would definitely stay here again. ", "date": "Reviewed May 28, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "Very good", "description": "Great hotel, nice staff, good location... just a lil dated and more attention to detail is needed. ", "date": "Reviewed Jun 3, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Great staff ", "date": "Reviewed Jun 1, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "Very good", "description": "Staff was very helpful  friendly & attentive. Room was XL compared to the regular tiny spaces elsewhere. Very close to the MTR station. Grateful for the free shuttle service to Star ferry. Lots of eateries around although expensive..with exception of the little dim sum place across the road. Altogether a very comfortable stay.  ", "date": "Reviewed May 25, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "As always, great service, perfect room, and great wine. I love staying at all Shangrila hotels when I travel abroad.", "date": "Reviewed May 16, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "Very good", "description": "good ", "date": "Reviewed May 21, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Excellent ", "date": "Reviewed May 20, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "My mum enjoyed very much when staying her hotel. I booked this hotel because this is convenient to the MTR and my mum likes the sea view. So glad that the hotel staff gave us a harbour view suite and few step distance due to my lift. My mum celebrated her 70th old birthday at Hong Kong and this hotel gives her a wonderful memories. I would like to thank the staff for the hospitality and we will come back again. ", "date": "Reviewed May 20, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "I'd incorrectly book down the first night of my stay but the staff found me a room, however it was a smoking one and quite smelly. Once I was in the pre booked rooms on the top floors with the Club it was very nice.  Our Conference was held in the hotel and the quality of facilities, service and food was excellent. There are also a range of ok bars and restaurants close by but it's all pricey. The hotel was good a providing regular shuttles to train and ferry wharves. So despite its age it's still a top business hotel.", "date": "Reviewed May 15, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "Very good", "description": "Great ocean front location with great views directly across onto Hong Kong Island. Walking distance to Nathan Street shopping and plenty of dining in all price ranges. ", "date": "Reviewed May 9, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "Very good", "description": "Spacious room, good furniture, good service, feel like at home,very comfortable for staying here. One of my favorite \r\nHotel.", "date": "Reviewed May 9, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "No stress on check-in & out. Very smooth. Bed makings are perfect. Hotel location is convenient to go shopping & go sightseeing. You can access to MTR East Tsim Sha Tsui & Tsim Sha Tsui station, Star Ferry pier on foot. Also there is a free shuttle bus for Kowloon station. When you go to the hotel or go to the airport, you can take it. You must find well hospitality and comfortable stay in Hong Kong with the hotel!!", "date": "Reviewed May 8, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Fantastic place with impeccable service and in a great location", "date": "Reviewed May 2, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "As always horizon club very good experience", "date": "Reviewed May 6, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "Very good", "description": "Didn\u2019t like the location but it was near the mtr.  Also made the bad choice of part harbour view room.  It was more like 1 part view of bad side of harbour and 4 parts view of office building.....", "date": "Reviewed Apr 28, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "It is my favorite place to stay for many years, for business or personal, always a pleasure!", "date": "Reviewed Apr 23, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "Very good", "description": "It is just ok for a 5* hotel.\r\nOne of the least modern and friendly Shangri la I have been to (7 countries at least).\r\nRooms are ok, though dated. Basic selection of tea and dehydrated coffee. No Nespresso machine.\r\nStaff is average. Ok but not smiling nor seeming committed or engaging.\r\nNothing that would make me come back really, except potentially the location, by the Tsim sua sui subway station, but all the hotels are nearby, so it is not a use here.\r\n\r\n", "date": "Reviewed Apr 15, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "It is very convenient to MTR and room is big, nice and clean. Above all , the staff are wonderful people across the board , from Guest relations , housekeeping to F & B outlet at Kool cafe.\r\nJust a special mention to Victor at Kool cafe who is always attentive and courteous at all times in spite of his heavy workrate. Also a lady who works in the egg section , very professional and always smiling.\r\nAll the housekeepers greet you and it makes you feel at home from home.\r\nCheers and a 5-star rating anytime to this hotel.\r\n\r\nThanks v much\r\nLewis", "date": "Reviewed Apr 14, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "one of the best experiences.genuine friendly attentive professional staff...excellent facilities..excellent food...excellent service  at tapas  restaurant and  health /fitness center.", "date": "Reviewed Apr 14, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "We have really enjoyed our stay with friendly and helpful staff.  The room has a nice view of the harbour.  The location is great with bus stops and MTR station nearby.", "date": "Reviewed Apr 13, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "having a harbor view and being on the horizon club floor makes your stay all the better", "date": "Reviewed Apr 10, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "Very good", "description": "The hotel is located across the street from a Starbucks\u2014perfect for cheap breakfast. Breakfast looked quite expensive at the hotel.  Our room was very clean, but I was surprised it didn\u2019t have a bathtub and the view was not at all my vision of Shangri-La! The concierge staff was very helpful and airport Express shuttle service was convenient. I was disappointed that the pool and locker room close at 10 pm. The hotel is a pretty long walk through underground tunnels to the subway station to get to Hong Kong Island. The ahistorical and Science museums are very close to the hotel. Lots of restaurants like Pizza Express, Outback and McDonald\u2019s nearby\u2014Pizza Express was best. Stay at this hotel if the price is right. ", "date": "Reviewed Apr 5, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "Very good", "description": "Good hotel near the sea front and shopping experience  will also come back", "date": "Reviewed Apr 3, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "6.0", "rating_badge": "Good", "description": "With the check in they requested an additional fee for my 15 year old son. Issue was resolved though Expedia and the hotel. However It was an unpleasant experience when you have paid for the entire 5 days and the hotel require further payment.", "date": "Reviewed Apr 1, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "Very good", "description": "Hotel was fine and the service in the club lounge was superb. But three times the wrong food was delivered at two of the restaurants on the property. The apology for the first and second mix up was acceptable and accepted but when it happened a third time it is hard not to see this as a complete lapse in management. The facilities were in general very good. ", "date": "Reviewed Mar 30, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "Very good", "description": "Great service/staff. Rooms are very very spacious. Easy location adjacent to the East TST station. Hotel does seem a bit dated compared to others in this price bracket? Think it works well for business travel, would be less inclined to book here for a personal trip", "date": "Reviewed Apr 1, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Perfect view of the harbour from our room, beds were very comfortable and the room was very clean. Attention to details is evident everywhere which made our stay most memorable. The location is perfect and very convenient to many shopping placess and MRT station.", "date": "Reviewed Mar 31, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Our second time staying at this Kowloon Shangri-La. Excellent hotel. Amazing service. Well situated. ", "date": "Reviewed Mar 13, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "First class hotel, great very helpful staff & facilities. Offered upgrade to Horizon Club, would thoroughly recommend if one is offered this. We were pampered for 5 days in the lounge with great breakfasts & evening drinks & canapes all with a fabulous view of Hong Kong Harbour. Met really nice fellow travellers from around the world there too. ", "date": "Reviewed Mar 10, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "This hotel has amazing hotel rooms. I stayed on the club level. The room size was immense. The service was excellent - right from the doorman to concierge. Some of the staff were not totally conversant in English. That was very strange for a 5-star hotel.\r\n\r\nAccess to club level was useful. The views of Victoria harbor from the Club (20th floor) were spectacular. Readily available coffee, muffins, snacks was useful. The views and service at the ground floor bar were also great\r\n\r\nThe location is perfect for tourists. It is not great for business as most of the offices are in Hong Kong Island (about 30 minutes by cab)", "date": "Reviewed Mar 9, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "great hotel to stay in.  the location is not as great for shopping, but view is amazing when the sky is clear.", "date": "Reviewed Mar 8, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Great location. The room with the bay view is anazing", "date": "Reviewed Feb 28, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Great location and great staff.  They took a personal interest in my daughter and I and made her first trip to the Kowloon/Hong Kong area a memorable one.  Thank you.", "date": "Reviewed Feb 17, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "This hotel was better than we had expected. The staff were friendly and helpful. The room was spacious and well designed. Everything was very clean and well looked after. We booked the Horizon Club package and this was excellent value. The hotel is in an excellent situation - very close to the MTR and shops and the ferry over to Hong Kong Island. The views from the breakfast area were exceptional, looking across the harbour to Hong Kong Island. We would have no hesitation in booking this hotel again.", "date": "Reviewed Feb 21, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "This  is a fantastic five-star hotel!  The lobby staff make checking in very efficient and pleasant! However, I have a minor complaint. The Housekeeping tends to be stingy with  replenishing coffee items, such as creamer, sugar, coffee, etc. I have to applaud the Engineering / Tech department  on going above and beyond helping me when I dropped my pedometer in the crevices of where the Wi-Fi was stored.", "date": "Reviewed Feb 19, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Hotel was lovely with good service. \r\nRoom very spacious and comfortable.  Great location which was quite good for sightseeing.  ", "date": "Reviewed Feb 12, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "I reserved a harbor view suite.  I thoroughly enjoyed th view of Hong Kong Island and all of the nautical activity in the harbor.  A bit pricey but well worth the money.", "date": "Reviewed Feb 4, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "The habour view room gives you the Hong Kong experince right there, the moment you walk in. At night is a whole new experience. The rooms are generous in size even with a king bed. The shower has great water pressure that will not disappoint. The funny quirk of this 5 star hotel is the room coffee facilities are like a 2 star budget hotel (coffee sashes and no milk) where as many others provide coffee machines. So close to a supermarket (turn left follow Moody Rd to K11 plaza) and other things. Plus the bonus of being on top of the East Tsim Sha Sui train station connecting to Tsim Sha Sui station, easy. Location is the key, close to the ferry terminal, supermarket, some local attractions, shuttle service, etc. The foyer lounge is relaxing place for (an expensive) drink. The cocktail bar needs some cocktail making training. Not far from a great breakfast restaurant on Kimberly Road (not Street) called 'Relax For A While' delicious congee. It was worth saving a little longer to stay in a harbour view room for a dreamy Hong Kong experience. ", "date": "Reviewed Jan 26, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Very nice hotel in Kowloon...great location near all the restaurants, shops and near the Hop On Hop Off bus and ferry. Large clean rooms , very quiet at night with high quality amenities. Room service was great...when we needed ice or towels....fast and friendly. I would recommend this hotel. ", "date": "Reviewed Jan 26, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Great Room (Harbor View on Lvl 18). Fantastic Breakfast spread. If any down side then the size of the pool but at least indoors.", "date": "Reviewed Jan 21, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "6.0", "rating_badge": "Good", "description": "Disappointed with the room, felt tired, smelt of damp and expected a bath for the high price", "date": "Reviewed Jan 8, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Stay was very good but your room rate is higher side.", "date": "Reviewed Jan 7, 2018"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "First we were impressed is the service - it\u2019s amazing. All staff is super friendly and nice. Breakfast is huge with many European American and Asian choices to eat, amazing choice of freshly squeezed juices, fresh sushi, fish, meat gourmet dishes. It was just impossible to try everything over our 3 nights stay. Another is location. If you get sea view room you can view all Hongkong from your bed including HK light show at 8pm every day. Steps from ferry that brings you to the other side of the city, HK cultural center, stars park and shopping. We were staying 3 days on our way to Thaliand and it was too short to enjoy. Wish to be back soon. Thanks so much for the amazing stay! ", "date": "Reviewed Dec 29, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "I am really happy stay here... I will stay in shangri la everywhere I go...", "date": "Reviewed Dec 28, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Excellent experience, all staff were very friendly. Very clean, comfortable. We got upgraded from half harbour view to full harbour view room. Would stay again.", "date": "Reviewed Dec 23, 2017"}
