{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Fantastic hotel with great service, exactly what you\u2019d expect from the Shangri-La. Great location in Kowloon, easily walkable to great restaurants and transit. Very complete gym. Breakfast is expensive but there is a Starbucks right across the street so would suggest going there instead.", "date": "Reviewed Dec 8, 2017"}
