{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "A little out of the way on Kowloon, but a great place to stay.  ", "date": "Reviewed Dec 12, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "The staff could not do enough to make my stay any better. Fantastic. ", "date": "Reviewed Dec 8, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "This hotel is top notch. From the entire staff to the room size and very spacious, and the hotel buffet. Everything you can think of a nice hotel, this is it. But the only issue I have is that if you are a Golden Circle member, do NOT book your stay through 3rd party web site. Instead book it direct with Shangri-La. Otherwise you will not earn your points during your entire stays. I lost my points for my 13 nights stay, alone with my dining points as well.", "date": "Reviewed Dec 7, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "6.0", "rating_badge": "Good", "description": "Not so good, especially the housekeeping, is not up to standards", "date": "Reviewed Nov 26, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "This is a top-of-the-line hotel in a great location with a stunning view over the harbour.  The staff were friendly and efficient.  Breakfast was not included and is pricey.", "date": "Reviewed Dec 4, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Overall great experience at this hotel with a quality staff that is always ready to help assist.  ", "date": "Reviewed Nov 14, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "This hotel's harbor view rooms and club are phenomenal.  All of the service staff from bellmen to servers to housekeeping are genuinely helpful and pleasant.  The rooms are elegantly designed and furnished.  Just a dream stay.", "date": "Reviewed Nov 7, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "From getting to th front door to getting back into our transport at the end of the stay I can\u2019t fault this hotel. \r\nThe staff , hotel in general first class, the view from our harbour facing view was world class. \r\nThe buffet restaurant was first class as was the Shang Palace . \r\nI couldn\u2019t recommend this hotel enough. \r\nThe staff make the place as well as the overall quality of the hotel. ", "date": "Reviewed Nov 12, 2017"}
