{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Staff is impeccable.\r\nIt all starts with the airport pickup, and the great treatment you will receive for the rest of your stay.\r\nNo one will treat you better than the people at the counter, restaurants, and Tapas bar.  They are\r\nthere to take care of your every need and will do it with cheer and a smile.\r\nGreat stay.", "date": "Reviewed Oct 14, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "The staff was really helpful given I speak no mandarin or Cantonese.   Everyone welcomed me and did their best to assist me.  The hotel is clean but maybe a little outdated.   The decor in the rooms could be improved.  Excellent location...minutes to metro, shopping, and entertainment  area.  I like to work out and the gym is awesome.   I would definitely stay here again.   ", "date": "Reviewed Oct 8, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Perfect for business. Beautiful desk in the room. fantastic breakfast. excellent overall", "date": "Reviewed Oct 7, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Nice helpful staff. Great food. Easy walk to the best spot for the light show.", "date": "Reviewed Sep 28, 2017"}
