{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "I really enjoyed my stay in this hotel.  Nice hotel staff and a reasonable distance from the airport.", "date": "Reviewed Sep 13, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "Very good", "description": "This not a new hotel, so it seems a bit dated. However, the rooms are very comfortable, service is excellent, though a little distant. All food options are very good, but a bit pricey.\r\nLocation is exceptional.  Rooms with a view have a soectacular view of Hong Kong and the bay.", "date": "Reviewed Sep 1, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "6.0", "rating_badge": "Good", "description": "service is not too bad, room is quite small for a 5* hotel ", "date": "Reviewed Sep 10, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "Very good", "description": "Great service by the staff. I left a purse at Tapas Bar but the staff handed it to concierge where I got it back.", "date": "Reviewed Sep 5, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Check in was easy and room was ready when we arrived.  Staff always available to help and recommend restaurants within walking distance of hotel.  ", "date": "Reviewed Sep 5, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "Very good", "description": "Classic Hong King hotel with class. Really enjoyed two nights I stayed", "date": "Reviewed Aug 25, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "We really enjoyed are stay at the Kowloon Shangri-La.  It is well located in Hong Kong.\r\n\r\nThe service was excellent  in all areas, but I would especially like to mention the bellman, doorman, and concierge.  They were very competent, friendly, and their suggestions made our stay better.\r\n\r\nThe Shang Palace restaurant was a special experience.  My daughter and I had dinner there and then came back for lunch the next day.  The food, especially the egg tarts, prawn curry, and crispy lobster, were amazing.  The manager did an excellent job helping us develop our own tasting menu and pairing the wines. The staff was attentive.\r\n\r\nWe also enjoyed tea or a drink in the lobby with the added benefit of music.\r\n\r\nI would highly recommend this hotel.\r\n", "date": "Reviewed Sep 3, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Fantastic staff as always at Shangri-la.\r\nSpecial mention to the amazing porter/bell boy team - nothing was too much trouble.\r\nHotel is a little dated, but I loved it anyway.", "date": "Reviewed Sep 1, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Great hotel. Large comfortable rooms with great view. Great service.", "date": "Reviewed Aug 26, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "Very good", "description": "Nice and clean hotel, totally feels like 5 star hotel. Close to the subway station", "date": "Reviewed Aug 28, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "We had a typhoon during our stay and staff were excellent in keeping us updated, they were concerned about our safety, and keptfoyer immaculate", "date": "Reviewed Aug 25, 2017"}
