{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "The grand, bright and modern entrance,  hospitality and friendliness of the hotel staff, excellent cleanness of the building area and our room, the excellent quality of food of restaurants and room- service, also being treated respectfully and in a friendly way by the staff and the hotel manager, all gave us a beautiful feeling of comfort, relaxation and unforgettable memory of our holiday during our stay in Shangri-La Kowloon. Million thanks.", "date": "Reviewed Aug 5, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Upgraded to the Horizon Club and it was well\r\nworth every penny. Fantastic appetizers and drinks\r\navailable all day long. In the incredible (read: oppressive) Hong Kong heat, having the Horizon Club to escape to was nirvana!", "date": "Reviewed Aug 5, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "coming from the USA you got to love this hotel and everything about it , location, service , and so much more , the service is exceptional they always open and hold the door for you and help you carry your luggage(even if you did not just arrive) or get a taxi and tell the cab driver your destination ,, rooms are very clean and nice, every evening  they will unfold your blanket and prepare bedtime snack  ,and help you in every way possible, free wifi good gym and pool , staff is super nice ,7-11 and starbucks right next door", "date": "Reviewed Jul 26, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "I loved it!!! Everyone was helpful and friendly. Excellent staff!", "date": "Reviewed Jul 27, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "Very good", "description": "It's the second time we stayed in this hotel while visiting Hong Kong, which means that it is good.", "date": "Reviewed Jul 30, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Great experience. Will go back for sure. Everything was perfect from start to finish.", "date": "Reviewed Jul 24, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "It was exceptional loved being there", "date": "Reviewed Jul 19, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "Very good", "description": "Great location, close to Metro, tapas restaurant a must specially for happy hour.  ", "date": "Reviewed Jul 16, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "This has to be one of the best hotels in the world. From the moment you step inside, until the moment you walk out--service, service, service!", "date": "Reviewed Jul 10, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "We just spent one night, the harbor is just steps away as well as the subway station and shops and restaurants.  Staff are friendly and helpful.  The only thing I can say is that the wifi is not code protected and open to the public.  The connection is not good in certain areas and security is another concern. For those who are new to Hong Kong, just want to let you know that humidity is high, which causes smell. ", "date": "Reviewed Jul 5, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "very good, it was nice place to stay in Hong Kong west  ", "date": "Reviewed Jul 1, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Very welcoming Hotel. Excellent place to stay. Central to most places around and close to the MTR to go to other places. Very Clean hotel. If you look closely they change the mats in the hotel everyday to match the day of the week.", "date": "Reviewed May 22, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Excellent service, very quiet rooms, very helpful staff -- 100% would return next time in HKG!", "date": "Reviewed May 31, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Very good hotel . Has everything you need and we'll located \r\nService was very good and excellent breakfast.", "date": "Reviewed May 27, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Classic hotel excellent location and service.  Really nice break after one week business trip in India. \r\nSubway right outside hotel.  Able to walk and explore area through underground subway exits right outside hotel.  One of the nicest service I have experienced around the world.  Would definitely stay again. ", "date": "Reviewed May 18, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "Very good", "description": "The hotel is well situated in Kow Loon relative to business, subways Star Ferry (little bit of a walk from the hotel) to Honk Kong, shopping and restaurants. The rooms are comfortable, mostly updated and have all the amenities mostr westerners would expect. The staff is exceptionally friendly and fluent in English and many other languages.\r\n\r\nI will be back.", "date": "Reviewed May 1, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "Very good", "description": "After sooo many years since 2006, many changes since the last trip.  Stayed in Hotel which is near to MTR and shopping centres.  Very enjoyable stay.  Will be going again sometime in March 2018 and staying at the same hotel.  Hopefully they will take into consideration of providing a room to use for about an hour to freshen up before flight home", "date": "Reviewed Apr 28, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Exceptional family trip with amazing service by the Horizon Club staff. Family of four with two small children sharing a harbour-view room on Club floor. Room was perfectly sized for our needs and breakfast and happy hour in the club lounge were ideal. Horizon Club staff (as well as all other Kowloon Shangri-la staff) were attentive and welcoming. This hotel is always a pleasure to return to.", "date": "Reviewed Apr 16, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "Very good", "description": "We've stayed at this hotel 3 times over the past two years, also tried the Regal and Intercontinental. The Shangri La is best overall in my mind: Nicer decor, cleaner, open-plan bar area with live music every evening. (Intercontinental's bar feels cramped and small in comparison). We'll definitely continue to stay here on our future visits.", "date": "Reviewed Apr 23, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Great location- very conveniently located and has magnificent views of the bay. Staff was ultra friendly. We paid more to be able to use the Horizon Club which we felt was well worth it. Had our morning breakfast and evening snacks there, and was able to enjoy the stunning views of the bay as our hotel room was on the opposite side. Only disappointment was the spa facility which we did not use anyways. We would definitely stay here again on any future trip to Hong Kong.", "date": "Reviewed Apr 20, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "This hotel is underrated. Service was excellent and over my expectations. Room was cleaned every time I left and was wonderful. Hotel is in wonderful shape. Staff is very friendly and curtious. I would recommend this hotel to anyone visiting Hong Kong.", "date": "Reviewed Apr 14, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Greeted by a welcoming front desk and impressive lobby. Was offered for an upgrade to harbour view (though at a cost). I am actually pleased that the staff did make that suggestion! The view from my room was just stunning! Room is clean and spacious, have everything I need and I got served with fruits and pot of tea. ;) MTR is just 5 mins walk away", "date": "Reviewed Apr 20, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Great hotel and location. Service is great! Made our stay gel special! ", "date": "Reviewed Apr 19, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "We arrived late (after a 12 hour flight delay) and everyone was helpful and quick to get us checked in and well looked after.\r\n", "date": "Reviewed Apr 9, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "It was surprisingly spacious room with large king bed & sofa with garden view. There are rooms with ocean view and it would be nice if we stay there. Large window with view of shopping area and small garden. A lot of light coming through window and very comfortable room. A lot of mirrors throughout room and bathroom, but the lighting is good so you don't mind having them. Free water bottles filled everyday and there was a hot water boiler so we made our own tea every day. It's walking distance to all sorts of restaurants, shopping, which is a must to stay in Hong Kong (Kawloon). We walked nearby beach and parks as well as we completed all shopping in the area. Though there were nice restaurants inside the hotel, which we tried once, you can walk down to have a typical Hong Kong style breakfast at very reasonable price and come back to room to have an additional tea time before going out. There is a large department store right next to it and you can make a custom made shirts delivered to the hotel in one day. Convenient for your friend to pick you up by car. Taxi is always available in front of hotel.", "date": "Reviewed Apr 7, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "A one week stay. Excellent hotel. Would recommend.  Comfortable, clean and nice ammenities", "date": "Reviewed Apr 6, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "Very good", "description": "Generally Good.  Close to everything.", "date": "Reviewed Mar 27, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "4.0", "rating_badge": "Fair", "description": "I booked a room for my dad on 22/03/17, but when he reached the hotel at 3pm, there was no available room. He was then told by the staff that the hotel was full for the type of room that was booked. I paid the full sum thru Expedia but in the end the staff of the hotel said that booked thru other website other than the Hotel itself is not guaranteed. He was then told to pay an extra S$300++ to upgrade to a better room in order to get a room immediately. We are very disappointed with the service.", "date": "Reviewed Mar 24, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "From the two staff waiting at the airport to take care of our large luggage to the waiting car ,on arrival at the hotel two more staff waiting at the door to check us in at our rooms not at the desk as we arrived late from Sydney ,all effortless for us then jasmine tea delivered .\r\nFinest smiling service from airport to our beautiful refurbished rooms with white Carrara marble .\r\nImpossible to beat ,smiling service with total comfort .\r\n", "date": "Reviewed Mar 22, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Very friendly staff, convenient location, good restaurants, clean room with view of harbor. Next to Tsim Sha Tsui East MTR station. Busy Tapas bar. ", "date": "Reviewed Feb 20, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Fantastic views of theh harbor great food\r\nAnd impeccable service", "date": "Reviewed Feb 10, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Great visit in Hong Kong, really enjoyed the location of Shangri La and their friendly staff!", "date": "Reviewed Feb 2, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "Very good", "description": "Very convenient location.  Train station is a few steps away.  Staff is very helpful,  food at Cafe Kool is ok, not as good as I expect.  Overall,  anot excellent hotel.", "date": "Reviewed Feb 1, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Greeted by a friendly member of staff - Margaret- who took us to the room and provided check in there, nothing was too much trouble. Provided excellent information on facilities and what was available during Chinese New Year,  a nice touch was Prosecco , dessert and fruit in the room as a thank you for choosing the hotel. This is the second time staying at the Shangri-la and will definitely stay again.  ", "date": "Reviewed Jan 28, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "We were very well received. Quiet room. We felt like we were the only ones in the hotel. Convenient location. Very professional staff. Food in the restaurants was great- to include Chinese selections. They also pay close attention to multi ethnic, religious, and medical requirements. Common allergens were listed in menus. Great experience. ", "date": "Reviewed Jan 26, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "From the picket the airport to the automated checkin and drop off at the airport, it was an overall great experience that i would 100% recommend.", "date": "Reviewed Jan 25, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "place is perfect.", "date": "Reviewed Jan 22, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Excellent hotel in Hong Kong.  Everything as expected of a luxury hotel.  Great breakfast. Nice staff. Gym is a bit crowded but they have good machines and in good condition.", "date": "Reviewed Jan 20, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "5 star hotel definitely worth a visit. General Manager is European and runs a tight ship.  Met him in the lobby and had a nice chat. Stayed on the club level. Excellent service and wonderful breakfast buffet. Only complaint is that the hotels airport van limo service is a little bit pricey. Suggest taking a taxi.", "date": "Reviewed Jan 14, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Absolutely beautiful, we would stay here again without a doubt.  Everything about this hotel was worthy of our highest rating and more.  The hotel is beautiful, the concierge services impeccable, train stations very convenient and restaurants delicious . Back side of the faces the Victoria Harbor.  It was so convenient and fun to bring in 2017.", "date": "Reviewed Jan 8, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "We had one night in Hong Kong and stayed at the Shangri- La and it was an experience to remember, the service was impecable the room and view of the harbour stunning and the staff were friendly, welcoming and very helpful.\r\nIt was approaching Christmas and the foyer and lobby were decorated and the atmosphere was  festive.\r\nWe will return.", "date": "Reviewed Jan 8, 2017"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "**. Early check in. So appreciated after long flight...The hotel is well decorated and has a classic Oriental look and presentation. The staff was friendly and courteous and helpful , and even kept our main luggage for us while we wait for flight  time... No hesitation to recommend this hotel to anyone.", "date": "Reviewed Dec 31, 2016"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Loved almost everything about hotel. Convenient to attractions and to transportation. Staff friendly and very accommodating. Cafe Kool restaurant was excellent. ", "date": "Reviewed Dec 30, 2016"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Very convenient location close to many nice restaurants and shops.  An easy walk to the Star Ferry for getting over to Hong Kong Island.", "date": "Reviewed Dec 19, 2016"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Perfect in every sense from the moment I arrived to being farwelled on my departure. The staff are amazing. Always met with smiles and professionalism. Concierge were brilliant in helping me find my way around Hong Kong using their public transport system which is extremely efficient. The Tapas bar was relaxing with great service as was the coffee lounge.The Shanghai Palace Restaurant was sensational. The food was delicious and gorgeous in presentation. I cannot find fault in any aspect of this hotel. I loved my stay at the Shangri-La.", "date": "Reviewed Dec 17, 2016"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Superb hotel, so close to all amenities. So clean and very friendly.  Upgrade to the horizon club, as you won't be disappointed. Brilliant breakfast looking over to Hong Kong island, evening cocktails and more, plus they give you a handy little portable Wifi device, brilliant when you're out and about, so quick too. We love staying here.", "date": "Reviewed Dec 4, 2016"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "The Shangri La Kowloon was opulent with friendly service.  Breakfast provided Asian and western foods in great variety. The location was walking distance to Star Ferry and many shopping areas.  We will definitely recommend staying here to everyone.", "date": "Reviewed Nov 30, 2016"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "If you are going to stay here, it is worth every penny to stay on the Horizon Club level in a harbor view room. From the moment you walk in to the hotel you are surrounded with friendly staff and a welcoming atmosphere. The experience at the Horizon club is leaps and bounds above any US 5-star hotel brand executive lounge. From the breakfast to afternoon tea, followed by cocktail hour in the evening, the club lounge offers spectacular views of Victoria Harbor while you enjoy exquisitely prepared dishes by the hotel's talented chefs. This hotel is the model of what a 5-star experience should be.", "date": "Reviewed Nov 26, 2016"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "A superb, outstanding hotel in all regards.", "date": "Reviewed Nov 15, 2016"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Very pleasant stay", "date": "Reviewed Nov 14, 2016"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Excellent property. Fantastic views of Hong Kong central and Victoria Harbour from harbour view room. Well worth it. Friendly and helpful staff. Room good size as well as bathroom. Train station/subway right across the road so easy access to get around. Only downside was the bed was on the hard side and not very comfortable. Pool is only a very small indoor pool within the health club gym area.", "date": "Reviewed Nov 13, 2016"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "The service from all staff levels are great. The location is good. The restaurants both Chinese and Japanese are great. Highly recommend to others especially for first time visit to Kowloon.", "date": "Reviewed Nov 11, 2016"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": null, "date": "Reviewed Nov 9, 2016"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "As a business we've usually stayed at either the Royal Garden or the Icon Exec rooms in TST East but with a tight budget we decided to go for none Exec rooms & also a change of hotel. We made the right decision with the Shangri-La. It's great hotel & the staff are so efficient & friendly. The facilities are very good & the Tapas bar was so good we didn't really miss the Exec room privileges. \r\nLocation wise it's very good & only a 15 min walk to the Star ferry or the Harbour shopping centre on Canton road. ", "date": "Reviewed Nov 9, 2016"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "The most considerate service was the night before check out day, the people would knock the door to ask if we need extra clean towels for next morning use.", "date": "Reviewed Nov 8, 2016"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Excellent service, the room was remarkably comfortable with great view of the Hong Kong harbor.  I will highly recommend the Shangri La Hotel.", "date": "Reviewed Nov 8, 2016"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "Very good", "description": "I greatly enjoyed my stay. Initially had a problem with check in. They spent a little time with that but JasonChung was very helpful and got us a great room. The breakfast was awesome ! The service was extremely courteous and friendly. Would love to recommend this to anyone", "date": "Reviewed Nov 7, 2016"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Great hotel \r\nLuxury hotel\r\nFood and drinks are too much expensive \r\nMini bar too\r\nGreat location", "date": "Reviewed Oct 20, 2016"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "Gave a low cost upgrade \r\ncos arrived early morning with breakfast, cocktails and afnoon tea included - amazing.", "date": "Reviewed Oct 28, 2016"}
{"rating_score": "8.0", "rating_badge": "Very good", "description": "Right by \u5c16\u6771\u7ad9 exit P also walkable distance to many local food shops, Michelin restaurants, and shopping area. Great staff, nice house keeping and front desk. Lobby cafe offers nice easy food and drink. I like the huge loop way outside lobby, provides many conveniency. You will know when you visit in a bad weather day... \r\n\r\nRoom was nice, though too close to the next building that I can't even open the curtain in day time.\r\n\r\nThe only set back during the stay was the over noisy lobby with running kids all over. Am I in a supermarket?...", "date": "Reviewed Oct 25, 2016"}
{"rating_score": "10.0", "rating_badge": "Exceptional", "description": "excellent property ideal place good service comfortable rooms. what else can one get? get the sea view rooms upper floor they are worth the price", "date": "Reviewed Oct 22, 2016"}
